label: The Daily Times
title: The_Daily_Times_(Malawi)
exrest: The Daily Times is a daily newspaper published in Blantyre, Malawi. It is the oldest newspaper in the country, founded by the monthly Central African Planter in 1895. Around 1900, the title Central African Times was adopted, and weekly publication. Later the title was changed again, to Nyasaland Times. With Malawian independence in 1964, it became simply The Times, and finally the Daily Times in 1972.
